# Quiz Inline Demo

## Introduction

This demonstrates how to embed quiz questions directly in your livebook markdown using the `<!-- quiz -->` marker.

## Setup

```elixir
Mix.install([{:kino, "~> 0.17.0"}])
```

```elixir
Code.require_file("quiz.ex", __DIR__)
```

